                            <div class="tags-block">
                                <p>
                                    Now one thing you are to remember is there a lot of tags and its good practice to be checking them from online
                                    resources since changes are made from time to time. Now to list a few
                                </p>
                                <div class="tags-def">
                                    <div class="selectors">
                                        <p style="margin-bottom: 4px;">html tag</p>
                                        <ul style="padding-left: 16px;">
                                            <li>
                                                <p style="margin-bottom: 4px;">head tag</p>
                                                <ul style="padding-left: 16px;">
                                                    <li>meta tags</li>
